theorem Topology.closure_eq_closure_interior_closure_of_P3
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : Topology.P3 (X := X) A) :
    closure (A : Set X) = closure (interior (closure A)) := by
  -- `closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A`
  have h₁ : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) :=
    closure_mono (interior_subset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A)
  -- `closure A ⊆ closure (interior (closure A))`, using `P3`
  have h₂ : closure (A : Set X) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) :=
    closure_mono (hA : (A : Set X) ⊆ interior (closure A))
  exact Set.Subset.antisymm h₂ h₁
